# Never ship these into the image.

# Secrets. A .env baked into an image is a leaked credential that follows the image
# everywhere it is pushed.
**/.env
**/.env.*

node_modules
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build

.git
.gitignore

# Sample CSVs and any real merchant data. The image must not carry PII.
sample/
**/*.csv

# Local scratch
**/*.log
**/coverage
**/.vscode
**/.idea

# Docs and dev-only files add nothing to a runtime image.
docs/
*.md
